The first part of these lines is Aaravi using meta-knowledge about the Pathfinder System calling its collections of monsters "Bestiaries", rather than D&D's term, "Monster Manuals". However, the Pathfinder Society actually exists within Golarion, and is a collection of adventurers, like Aaravi, so it would be fair for Arue to assume she's talking about the Society rather than being confused about the game system that she wouldn't know about. Not to tell you how to write your own character or anything, just a lore note and suggestion
